# ClaudeMaxxersClub / skill-networker — gitignore
#
# Rule: framework gets committed, user-specific CONTEXT stays local.
# Everything here is designed to keep private user data out of the
# shared canon while still letting the skill run locally against
# populated files.

# Private library content (user-specific profile and warm network notes).
# Templates and the README are committed; everything else is local-only.
library/*.md
!library/*.template.md
!library/README.md

# Private runtime config (output paths, notification bot tokens, etc).
config.yaml

# Generated outputs if the skill writes into its own folder (unusual; default
# output path is ~/Documents/person-intel/).
output/
dossiers/

# OS and editor cruft
.DS_Store
*.swp
*~
.vscode/
.idea/
